{"tid":1811653,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解熱青城班咁多低智，原來佢地主張有病都唔會睇醫生，燒壞埋個腦","createTime":"2020-01-05T00:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T16:31:49.000Z","uid":122208,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4005675e56c0132ff615c28c82062865ebfb799f","tid":1811653,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T00:41:40.000Z","msg":"點解熱青城班咁多低智<br />\n原來佢地主張有病都唔會睇醫生，燒壞埋個腦<br />\n<br />\n先唔講陳雲，佢d信徒水晶姥姥，熱狗Billie ng喱班on9老母，自己個仔病，都會等佢地自己好番<br />\n<br />\n喱班仆街熱青城最鐘意講自然療法，睇醫生就係on9喎<br />\nBillie NG 水晶姥姥 話發燒都唔會睇醫生㗎<br />\n等自己自動復原<br />\n網民提相反意見，會俾佢地水泥隊圍屌<br />\n希望佢地今次都忠於自己啦，中招咪等自己復原<br />\n死左唔好問點解<br />\n同奉勸一句，自己冚家死埋係屋企<br />\n咪出街傳染俾正常香港人（即係非熱狗）"},{"pid":"525783bcc9ec4372a7c48409b249d5ade63bdd5e","tid":1811653,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T00:43:14.000Z","msg":"乜都屌一餐嘅失敗主義撚<br />\n關鍵時候就奶共，同中共口徑一致，叫你投白票射落海嘅仆街<br />\n<br />\n推到比立場/蘋果/議員睇到<br />\n［停止使用建制稱呼親共人士］<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQscQho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQscQho.jpg&h=56da94ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求使用「共派」取代「建制」稱呼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1811104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1811104</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd9b9e6b28b4f715f88e2a040568de95857d454f","tid":1811653,"uid":264387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T00:44:49.000Z","msg":"其實我都係，感冒低燒等自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30dfa209ac67ab8772a819ef15eea5d522b47f8","tid":1811653,"uid":224625,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cd9b9e6b28b4f715f88e2a040568de95857d454f","tid":1811653,"uid":264387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T00:44:49.000Z","msg":"其實我都係，感冒低燒等自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla