811653,"uid":233643,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:20:26.000Z","msg":"其實連登仔真係好多弱智白痴<br />\n人地成篇野重點係講緊deep state 講深層國家如何透過研發/故意放出病毒<br />\n或者係本身無咩事既疾病故意比佢地放大 等人為左去治療而要花極大量金錢<br />\n姐係重點係講班大藥廠之類點樣透過創造疾病黎刮你地市民一大筆<br />\n但連登仔既理解係 病左唔好睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始明點解人地要set個智力門檻了<br />\n連登仔無果個門檻真係唔好學人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b6d03264fd132487acfa958e1902e1029c1961","tid":1811653,"uid":337899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"熱狗症"}]}